FBIS4-20253 "drweu083_j_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-083 Daily Report 28 Apr 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Berlusconi Asked To Form Government Berlusconi Asked To Form Government LD2804162694 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1602 GMT 28 Apr 94 LD2804162694 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Italian BFN [Text] The head of state has given the task of forming the new government to Forza Italia leader Silvio Berlusconi. The Right Honorable Berlusconi has reserved his decision to accept the task.
